items.narrative: Inherited real estate (a hotel) from father in 70s
Started work at Roche and rose to be senior VP of new products (2M CHF in stock options)
Sold real estate in 2000 for 20M CHF

items.headline: Google shares hit an all-time high after the companys quarterly report
items.summary: Google shares surged to a record high Friday after the Internet-search giant showed signs of quelling two big investor concerns: Can it make money from mobile phones and can it be managed with more discipline?

items.narrative: Used proceeds from sale of company to start a new pharmaceutical firm based in Basel
